{"tid":1559970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，醒下啦！你地輸L撚左啦！","createTime":"2019-09-11T04:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T05:04:43.000Z","uid":294847,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a99648c7e8c334537a30dbe2653c225e1693a42a","tid":1559970,"uid":294847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:43:34.000Z","msg":"612 721 831<br />\n9位自殺<br />\n多人被自殺<br />\n過千被捕<br />\n爆眼&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊仲有文革式批鬥報案，<br />\n買警棍，<br />\n以今時嘅手法， 完全唔需要有委任證，有棍就是警。<br />\n<br />\n咁多問題， 我哋仲要&quot;忍&quot; 到幾時？<br />\n國歌？撚狗？死線？<br />\n<br />\n冇錯歌係可以振奮士氣，團結人心， 認同感。但係唱完呢？屋企瞓覺？<br />\n<br />\n到底最近係畀狗撚？定係我哋撚狗？<br />\n作首歌咁多個版本，最後都係過下口癮<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775/permalink/1781105888898436/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F295202647488775%2Fpermalink%2F1781105888898436%2F&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReooeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=f85956a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/295202647488775/permalink/1781105888898436/</a><br />\n<br />\n最後畀人笑返轉頭！！ 笑你地縮翻入阿媽個西到咋！！<br />\n<br />\n死線？ 每次死線最後，都有手足被捕，每次都係頭破血流！！<br />\n到底幾時先係真正嘅死線？<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以唔好再將手足&quot;<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">英雄化</span></span>&quot; 住？<br />\n留到最後勝利先？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W7TSgCy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW7TSgCy.jpg&h=d4684ed4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/8413498154/permalink/10156912962803155/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F8413498154%2Fpermalink%2F10156912962803155%2F&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReooeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=a0805128\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/8413498154/permalink/10156912962803155/</a><br />\n<br />\n冇錯係要記住佢地嘅英勇， 但唔係以咁樣嘅方式， 條片睇到最後原來係得兩隻狗？ 唔係佢哋好英勇，係你哋過份<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">懦弱</span></span>！！ 點解冇人返轉頭救佢地？ 你哋將佢應英雄化有意思咩？ 換來嘅係咩？一句多謝年輕人，好感動？ 我相信佢哋而家畀人捉咗去邊，咩刑罰，都冇人知呀！！！！！<img src=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/8413498154/permalink/10156912962803155/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F8413498154%2Fpermalink%2F10156912962803155%2F&h=214054c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上前線嘅人越嚟越少，小小事就走嘅人越嚟越多， 咁樣流失法， 最後就只有永續社運， 甚至完全滅聲， 批鬥已經殺到嚟啦，求下你地醒啦好嗎&hellip;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好再分所謂和理非，勇武，我呢一齊邁前啦&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">何解血在留， 但邁進聲響透， 建自由光輝香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔係何解血在流，但逃跑聲響透<br />\n<br />\n已經三個月， 我哋已經證明到我哋嘅團結，我期待真正嘅升級會到來&hellip;<br />\n改變啦，香港人，攞出你哋嘅決心&hellip;<br />\n我係前線等你地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不割蓆 <br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n武裝起義<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"9725eb87b66c1bba5cd84f92ccf931bd17a3e43e","tid":1559970,"uid":294847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:46:38.000Z","msg":"P仔推唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8309719791a63c5ba6bed23e27c8e5926c61418a","tid":1559970,"uid":294847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233a0d2cf0ad794e03d2a0399610d3fb907934bb","tid":1559970,"uid":294847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20